[1] Global update: Polio Eradication Initiative
Date: Wed 14 Nov 2012
Source: Global Polio Eradication Initiative [excerpted, edited]
http://www.polioeradication.org/Dataandmonitoring/Poliothisweek.aspx


Global Polio Eradication Initiative update as of 14 Nov 2012
---------------------------------------------
Total cases
Year-to-date 2012 / Year-to-date 2011 / Total in 2011*
Globally: 187 / 520 / 650
- in endemic countries: 182 / 241 / 341
- in non-endemic countries: 5 / 279 / 309

Case breakdown by country
Country: Year-to-date 2012 WPV1 / WPV3 / W1W3 / Total // Year-to-date 2011 WPV1 / WPV3 / W1W3 / Total // Total in 2011* / Date of most recent case
Pakistan: 51 / 2 / 1 / 54 // 143 / 2 / 0 / 145 // 198 / 27 Oct 2012
Afghanistan: 27 / 0 / 0 / 27 // 53 / 0 / 0 / 53 // 80 / 1 Oct 2012
Nigeria: 83 / 18 / 0 / 101 // 23 / 9 / 0 / 42 // 62 / 15 Oct 2012
India: 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 // 1 / 0 / 0 / 1 // 1 / 13 Jan 2011
Chad: 5 / 0 / 0 / 5 // 114 / 3 / 0 / 117 // 132 / 14 Jun 2012
DR Congo: 0 / 0/ 0 / 0 // 86 / 0 / 0 / 86 // 93 / 20 Dec 2011
